
Installation of Angular 
Step-1
    first install typescript
    In windows: npm install -g typescript
    In ubantu : sudo npm install -g typescript
Step-2
    Angular App
    sudo npm install -g angular-cli
    
    using the seed from the github
    To create the skeleton for the angular
    git clone https://github.com/angular/quickstart.git quickstart
   
Step-3
  
  Installation of npm
  npm install
  
Step -4
  for starting the sever in local
  npm start
